          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
            <span class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] font-700 mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>We do not accept diabetic cats</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
            <span class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] font-700 mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>Cats sharing a cabin must all be from the same household</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">
            <span class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] font-700 mt-0.5">•</span>
