        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-soft)]">Full terms and conditions are available on our <a href="/3222/terms-conditions-html" class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] underline">Terms &amp; Conditions page</a>.</p>
